Singer Tamar Braxton has reportedly been rushed to hospital after her boyfriend found her unresponsive in a LA hotel they were staying in together in LA. MailOnline reports that when her boyfriend David Adefeso found her, he immediately called 911. The site also quoted him as saying that she had been drinking and had taken an unknown number of prescription pills in what he believes was an "attempted suicide". Meanwhile, her spokesperson told the publication that she'd had a tough day. "She had a tough and emotional day. More information will follow in the next few days. Please pray for her," the singer's spokesperson said.